about what I do. you here.

759
00:42:48.374 --> 00:42:49.792
workin' for me.

760
00:42:51.460 --> 00:42:53.045
I'm workin' with my dad.

761
00:42:53.629 --> 00:42:54.505
My bad.

762
00:42:54.672 --> 00:42:55.631
Right.

763
00:42:56.090 --> 00:42:57.675
You workin' with Marvin.

764
00:42:58.801 --> 00:43:00.136
Ain't got shit to do with me.

765
00:43:04.598 --> 00:43:06.267
You funny. Juke.

766
00:44:03.491 --> 00:44:04.700
Yo.

767
00:44:45.908 --> 00:44:48.869
How come you look better
every time I see you?

768
00:44:48.994 --> 00:44:51.163
'Cause your eyes
keep getting worse.

769
00:45:21.777 --> 00:45:23.612
My Scooby Snacks have arrived.

770
00:45:28.867 --> 00:45:30.619
Gonna be a late one tonight.

771
00:46:01.066 --> 00:46:03.819
Riff got another job for you.

772
00:46:03.944 --> 00:46:05.946
Can't. Flossie hit me.

773
00:46:06.071 --> 00:46:09.158
I got a trick across town.
New guy. Can't be late.

774
00:46:23.672 --> 00:46:25.215
Spoke to Pastor Evans today.

775
00:46:27.593 --> 00:46:29.094
What's Pastor sayin'?

776
00:46:29.261 --> 00:46:31.472
Mostly just listened
to me talk about Lou.

777
00:46:32.014 --> 00:46:33.932
But he did tell me
I need to find God.

778
00:46:34.391 --> 00:46:35.434
Course he did.

779
00:46:36.352 --> 00:46:37.895
That's the business he in.

780
00:46:40.648 --> 00:46:41.815
You believe in God?

781
00:46:47.071 --> 00:46:48.238
Shit.

782
00:46:49.740 --> 00:46:50.991
I don't know.

783
00:46:53.744 --> 00:46:55.037
Sometimes.

784
00:46:56.038 --> 00:46:58.248
I do. I believe in him.

785
00:46:59.416 --> 00:47:02.753
I mean. it can't just be all
this shit happen by accident.

786
00:47:02.920 --> 00:47:04.421
Someone placed us here
for a reason.

787
00:47:04.588 --> 00:47:07.216
Somebody gotta have
a bigger plan for us

788
00:47:07.341 --> 00:47:09.718
than just this bullshit.

789
00:47:12.096 --> 00:47:13.097
Maybe so.

790
00:47:13.972 --> 00:47:16.809
I mean. when shit get ill.

791
00:47:18.268 --> 00:47:21.146
and it seem like...

792
00:47:22.940 --> 00:47:24.400
you ain't got nothin' left.

793
00:47:25.234 --> 00:47:26.610
you start prayin'.

794
00:47:27.695 --> 00:47:31.073
You ain't prayin' to the mayor
or the fuckin' president.

795
00:47:31.532 --> 00:47:33.617
or even Mama to save you.

796
00:47:34.326 --> 00:47:35.786
You prayin' to God.

797
00:47:36.370 --> 00:47:38.706
But maybe you prayin' like that
'cause you so pressed.

798
00:47:38.872 --> 00:47:40.749
start reachin' for shit
that ain't true.

799
00:47:40.916 --> 00:47:43.752
Or maybe you so pressed that...

800
00:47:44.628 --> 00:47:46.213
you finally reach the truth.

801
00:47:49.883 --> 00:47:51.927
Shit. Fuck if I know.

802
00:47:52.052 --> 00:47:54.847
Just feel like I'm lookin'
for some shit I lost

803
00:47:55.597 --> 00:47:57.474
and I know I'm never
gonna find it.

804
00:48:06.358 --> 00:48:07.651
Keep lookin' anyway.

805
00:48:11.113 --> 00:48:13.115
It ain't even about just Lou.

806
00:48:14.283 --> 00:48:16.368
It's about us.
It's about everything.

807
00:48:17.578 --> 00:48:18.746
Maybe...

808
00:48:19.121 --> 00:48:20.581
we all lost. Raq.

809
00:48:21.248 --> 00:48:22.541
And maybe...

810
00:48:25.169 --> 00:48:26.754
we ain't never gon' be found.

811
00:48:51.653 --> 00:48:53.322
<i>You do this shit
long enough.</i>

812
00:48:53.447 --> 00:48:55.032
<i>one thing's for sure.</i>

813
00:48:55.199 --> 00:48:57.284
<i>Your circle gonna get
a hell of a lot smaller.</i>

814
00:48:57.951 --> 00:49:00.454
<i>You gon' lose damn near
every nigga you ever trusted.</i>

815
00:49:00.621 --> 00:49:01.955
What's your name?

816
00:49:02.456 --> 00:49:04.666
Whatever you want it to be.

817
00:49:05.417 --> 00:49:06.710
<i>And as tough
as it is to lose</i>

818
00:49:06.877 --> 00:49:08.420
<i>all your old friends...</i>

819
00:49:09.254 --> 00:49:10.964
<i>the shit you really need
to worry about</i>

820
00:49:11.924 --> 00:49:13.258
<i>is your new ones.</i>

821
00:49:14.802 --> 00:49:16.595
<i>'Cause you can't trust
new friends. nigga.</i>

822
00:49:17.346 --> 00:49:18.305
<i>Not ever.</i>
